## STEP 7 — Open PowerShell inside your project
```
1. Open File Explorer
2. Navigate to: C:\Users\ahmed\Desktop\Flutter Projects\swiftcart
3. Click the address bar at the top
4. Type "powershell" and press Enter
   ↳ This opens PowerShell directly inside your project folder